title: The Chopped Leaf
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Western, Salad bar, Take-out, Catering, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Quick service franchise with several locations offering salads, wraps, sandwiches, and soups. While pre-set menu items are not veg, you can design your own salads and wraps to make it veg or vegan. Has smoked tofu.
